{"type":null,"faqId":14030,"title":"如何使用设备找回功能？","answer":"<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在遗忘或丢失荣耀</span><span> X1\n7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">时，设备找回功能能够帮助您定位荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当前所处的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"gen-id1.4.14.2.2\"></a><span style=\"color:#339966;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44750\" width=\"57\" height=\"16\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin:0 0 0 40px;border:none;padding:0px;\">\n  <p>\n    <span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">您的荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">需满足以下几个条件才可以使用设备找回功能：</span>\n  </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">是开机状态且已连接至互联网</span><span>;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">已经在荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">上登录了华为帐号；</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">中<b>手机找回</b>功能已开启。您可以在主屏幕上点击<b>同步</b>，在<b>管控</b>区域开启<b>手机找回</b>功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"figd0e1290\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44751\" width=\"531\" height=\"478\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>1.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span> PC </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">端登录</span><span> www.hicloud.com</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，进入云服务首页。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>2.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在云服务首页点击<b>手机找回</b>，在弹出的对话框中输入云帐户密码即可在网页端管控您的荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设备找回功能需要连接网络，定位成功后，在网页上会显示荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当前所在的位置。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您还可以远程向</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">发送警告信息、锁定</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、备份数据和清除数据等，以减少不必要的损失。</span>\n</p>","faqTypeId":171,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":1,"unUseful":8,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5690","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1406078775000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":541,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"平板丢失,找回","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}